<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,342,1746,1770]" pageId="2" pageNumber="50">FIGURES 1–18.</emphasis>
Types of skipper taxa described by Jinhaku Sonan: 1–3, holotype of 
<taxonomicName box="[1115,1307,1746,1769]" class="Insecta" family="Hesperiidae" genus="Lobocla" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="50" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="kodairai">
<emphasis box="[1115,1307,1746,1769]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="50">Lobocla kodairai</emphasis>
