, upperside, underside, labels; 13–15, holotype of 
<taxonomicName box="[283,574,1850,1873]" class="Insecta" family="Hesperiidae" genus="Ampittia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="50" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subSpecies" species="maro" subSpecies="matsumurai">
<emphasis box="[283,574,1850,1873]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="50">Ampittia maro matsumurai</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, upperside, underside, labels; 16–18. holotype of 
<taxonomicName box="[1118,1429,1850,1873]" class="Insecta" family="Hesperiidae" genus="Augiades" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="50" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subSpecies" species="bouddha" subSpecies="niitakana">
<emphasis box="[1118,1429,1850,1873]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="50">Augiades bouddha niitakana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, upperside, underside, labels.
